@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.50) - wp.sin(v0 + 0.15)) + 0.80)
    v0 = 0.35
    tmp = 0.08
    v1 = 0.86
    tmp = (v1 * wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.55)))
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.abs(tmp + 0.10) - wp.sin(v0 + 0.16)))
    data[tid] = v0
